---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Accessibility Statement"
  description="AVL Curious's commitment to web accessibility, target conformance, and how to report issues."
  noindex={true}
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 sm:py-20 prose">
    <h1 class="font-display text-mountain-900">Accessibility Statement</h1>
    <p class="text-mountain-500"><em>Draft — last updated 2026-05-05.</em></p>

    <p>AVL Curious is committed to making this site usable for everyone, including people with disabilities. We design and build to <strong>WCAG 2.1 Level AA</strong>.</p>

    <h2>What we do</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Keyboard navigation throughout the site, including a skip-to-content link.</li>
      <li>Visible focus indicators on every interactive element.</li>
      <li>Color contrast tested against WCAG AA thresholds.</li>
      <li>Alt text on every meaningful image; semantic markup for headings, lists, and forms.</li>
      <li>Forms with explicit labels and clear error messaging.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Known limitations</h2>
    <p>This site is in active development. If you find an accessibility barrier, please tell us.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>To report an accessibility issue or request an alternative format for any content, email <a href="mailto:karin@fuzzywolfsales.com">karin@fuzzywolfsales.com</a> or call <a href="tel:+12017256428">(201) 725-6428</a>. We aim to respond within two business days.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
